{"id":324276,"type":2,"name":"ブタヅカ","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/9f/ef/324276_U66Fk.jpg","summary":"――ここは国全体が世界特別自然保護区に指定された南米パナビアン共和国。\r\n北西部に広がるジャングルには全長8cmほどの奇妙な生態を持った生物が存在する。\r\nそれが幻の動物“プチブタ”だ。\r\n今だにその生態のなぞは明らかにされていない。\r\n“プチブタ”は“ブタヅカ”と呼ばれる巨大な塚を形成し、女王ブタを頂点としたシロアリに似た社会構造を持つ生き物である。\r\nこの物語は“ブタヅカ”の第一発見者でもある研究者が、その生涯を“ブタヅカ”研究に捧げて撮った、生態観察ドキュメンターリー映像である...。――","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>13</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2005-11-10</li><li><span>别名: </span>Butazuka</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>https://www.tv-asahi.co.jp/ch/contents/anime/0359/</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"dropped":2},"eps":[{"id":999673,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999673","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999674,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999674","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999675,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999675","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999676,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999676","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999677,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999677","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999678,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999678","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999679,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999679","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999680,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999680","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999681,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/999681","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":999682,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/99